 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person who growsiris is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the person who growsrose is between the person who growszinnia and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
13. the person who growslily is between the person eating strawberry and the person who growsamaryllis##2
14. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the person eating broccoli is between the person driving the ship and the person eating artichoke##2

